data.description: Extraordinary home blends spacious, open concept living with updates, convenience & LAKE VIEWS! Boasting 3,152 sq ft, it's the one! This light-filled main level welcomes you with a 2 story grand entry, features recently updated custom kitchen with solid surface counters & center island overlooking remodeled expansive living space completed by flex room. Upstairs enjoy an oversized master suite with freshly updated bath, vaulted ceiling, spacious walk-in closet & lake views, 3 guest rooms & guest bath. Finished lower level includes a beautiful guest suite, massive rec room, bath & extra built in work space. Outside find a beautiful lake view corner lot with privacy fenced backyard completed by a newly added expansive deck perfect for play & entertaining! Centrally located, minutes to Scott AFB & conveniences. Recent updates/additions: finished basement, appliances, water heater, counters, cabinet refinishing, master bath, flooring, paint, lighting, water softener, deck & fence! WOW!
